      "span_text": "By combining this dataset with results from the same raccoon sample that had previously been generated for the MHC class II, we obtained strong evidence for an interaction between the variables MAADiv of MHC class I and MAADiv of MHC class II of candidate males on their probability of being chosen by any female as a mating partner ( p-value ¼ 5.1 Â 10 25 )."
